36
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:17,380
love and take care of her (Kazakh language).

37
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,500
But what if (Kazakh language)

38
00:03:21,920 --> 00:03:23,450
this boy (Kazakh language)

39
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,400
is already engaged (Kazakh language),

40
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:27,460
what should he do (Kazakh language)?

41
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:33,300
Are you talking about yourself (Kazakh language)?

42
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,640
Yes, Father (Kazakh language).

43
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:40,200
She likes me (Kazakh language),

44
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,560
