45
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,560
I think I've fallen in love with her (Kazakh language).

46
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,760
What's wrong with you (Kazakh language)?

47
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:48,290
What nonsense about love (Kazakh language)?

48
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:54,160
Samukhar (Kazakh language)

49
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:56,840
I know (Kazakh language)

50
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:59,930
you don't have feelings for Ayim (Kazakh language).

51
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:02,840
But Ayim is also a good girl (Kazakh language).

52
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:06,400
We shouldn't hold her happiness hostage (Kazakh language).

53
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:13,000
Where are you going (Kazakh language)?

54
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,860
Where can I go (Kazakh language)?

55
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:16,720
To Ayim's father's house (Kazakh language),

56
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:18,839
to apologize to them (Kazakh language),

57
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:21,760
and seek their forgiveness (Kazakh language).

58
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,840
What if this girl (Kazakh language)

59
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:27,700
