Samukhar brother (Kazakh)

61
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:05,300
Why are you here? (Kazakh)

62
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:07,680
Ayim (Kazakh)

63
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:11,160
