69
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:35,880
Who are you talking about (Kazakh)

70
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:36,680
Zhenzhu?

71
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:42,570
I wish you happiness. (Kazakh)

