78
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,840
Brother Samuhar. (Kazakh)

79
00:06:43,840 --> 00:06:45,520
What's so special about her? (Kazakh)

80
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:46,920
Can she ride horses? (Kazakh)

81
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:47,920
Can she drink? (Kazakh)

82
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:50,120
Can she live with you in a yurt? (Kazakh)

83
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,140
What is she saying?

84
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,570
She says you're beautiful.

85
00:06:58,159 --> 00:07:00,020
