87
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,800
Of course I can.

88
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,780
Ayim. (Kazakh)

89
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,700
Do you dare to compete with me?

90
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,640
If I win,

